options.markdown:
RED Metrics by Service R - Requests
E - Errors
D - Duration

chart.name: Abandonment Rate
chart.programText:
A = data('sf_demo.num_calls', rollup='sum').sum().sum(over='1d').publish(label='A', enable=False)
C = (A*.0000034).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (A*.000005).publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (C/D).scale(100).publish(label='E')

chart.name: Abandonment Rate by Device
chart.programText:
A = data('sf_demo.num_calls', filter=filter('device_type', 'Mobile Phone', 'Wearable', 'GPS'),rollup='rate').sum(by=['device_type']).mean(over='5m').publish(label='A', enable=False)
C = (4/A*10000).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Cost per API Call
chart.programText:
A = data('sf_demo.num_calls', filter=filter('service', 'deposit'),rollup='rate').sum(by=['aws_instance_id', 'service']).count().scale(0.42).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A/60).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = data('sf_demo.num_calls', filter=filter('service', 'deposit'), rollup='sum').sum().sum(over='1m').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (B/C).publish(label='D')
E = data('sf_demo.num_calls', filter=filter('service', 'transfer'),rollup='rate').sum(by=['aws_instance_id', 'service']).count().scale(0.665).publish(label='E', enable=False)
F = (E/60).publish(label='F', enable=False)
G = data('sf_demo.num_calls', filter=filter('service', 'deposit'), rollup='sum').sum().sum(over='1m').publish(label='G', enable=False)
H = (F/G).publish(label='H')
I = data('sf_demo.num_calls', filter=filter('service', 'withdraw'),rollup='rate').sum(by=['aws_instance_id', 'service']).count().scale(0.266).publish(label='I', enable=False)
J = (I/60).publish(label='J', enable=False)
K = data('sf_demo.num_calls', filter=filter('service', 'withdraw'), rollup='sum').sum().sum(over='1m').publish(label='K', enable=False)
L = (J/K).publish(label='L')

chart.name: p99 Latency by Region
chart.programText:
A = data('sf_demo.mean_latency_ms').percentile(pct=99, by=['region']).scale(100).publish(label='A')
B = events(eventType='code_deploy').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/A).scale(2800).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = events(eventType='DGAkhbpAgAA__P99 API Latency has suddenly changed for 1 or more services').publish(label='D')

chart.name: Errors vs. Abandonment Rate
chart.programText:
A = data('sf_demo.num_calls', rollup='sum').sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
E = (A/10000).publish(label='E')
C = (A/2).scale(0.01).timeshift('15s').mean(over='1m').publish(label='C')

chart.name: # Hosts vs. Latency vs. Abandonment Rate
chart.programText:
A = data('sf_demo.num_calls',rollup='rate').min().publish(label='A', enable=False)
C = (10000/A).publish(label='C')
D = (A/2).mean(over='5m').scale(0.1).publish(label='D')
E = (A/2).mean(over='10m').scale(0.1).publish(label='E')
F = data('sf_demo.num_calls', rollup='sum').sum().publish(label='F', enable=False)
G = (F/2).scale(0.01).publish(label='G', enable=False)
